To make the Cake: Preheat oven to 350 degrees F. Spray sides and bottom of a bundt pan with vegetable cooking spray, or grease with butter or margarine. Combine dry cake mix with oil, eggs, and nutmeg. Mix in 1 cup of LACTAID(R) EggNog in place of water (regardless of the amount of water called for on the package). Bake for 35 minutes. Cool. To make EggNog Glaze: Combine sugar with margarine or butter in a medium bowl; add vanilla. Add enough LACTAID(R) EggNog for desired consistency.